ability. Until then, it's just another shiny tool in t https://t.co/q25Z7ipl8C","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":5},"author_id":"1656969601648066560","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:55.000Z","id":"2040550206899409192"},{"entities":{"urls":[{"start":70,"end":93,"url":"https://t.co/Vl37uxQ4j9","expanded_url":"https://www.theverge.com/ai-artificial-intelligence/907074/anthropic-openclaw-claude-subscription-ban","display_url":"theverge.com/ai-artificial-…","images":[{"url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2040216589413552128/a_Mn3BwN?format=jpg&name=orig","width":1200,"height":624},{"url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2040216589413552128/a_Mn3BwN?format=jpg&name=150x150","width":150,"height":150}],"status":200,"title":"Anthropic essentially bans OpenClaw from Claude by making subscribers pay extra","description":"Claude vs. Claw.","unwound_url":"https://www.theverge.com/ai-artificial-intelligence/907074/anthropic-openclaw-claude-subscription-ban"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040550170820026776"],"text":"\uD83E\uDD16 Anthropic限制Claude订阅用于第三方工具OpenClaw，AI商业生态管控趋严，开发者须额外付费才能继续使用，行业格局或生变https://t.co/Vl37uxQ4j9","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":0},"author_id":"2033463318401482752","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:46.000Z","id":"2040550170820026776"},{"entities":{"urls":[{"start":131,"end":154,"url":"https://t.co/lXrwHznQJT","expanded_url":"https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=47633396","display_url":"news.ycombinator.com/item?id=476333…","status":200,"title":"Anthropic no longer allowing Claude Code subscriptions to be used with OpenClaw | Hacker News","description":"Received the following email from Anthropic: Hi, Starting April 4 at 12pm PT / 8pm BST, you’ll no longer be able to use your Claude subscription limits for third-party harnesses including OpenClaw. You can still use them with your Claude account, but they will require extra usage, a pay-as-you-go option billed separatel y from your subscription. Your subscription still covers all Claude products, including Claude Code and Claude Cowork. To keep using third-party harnesses with your Claude login, turn on","unwound_url":"https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=47633396"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040550139757252749"],"text":"Tell HN: Anthropic no longer allowing Claude Code subscriptions to use OpenClaw。OpenClawで自動化してて思うのは、ツールの賢さより運用設計が先。みんなはどこから手をつけてる？ https://t.co/lXrwHznQJT","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":8},"author_id":"2038317470185082880","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:39.000Z","id":"2040550139757252749"},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040550073604718964"],"text":"AnthropicがClaude","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":1,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":0},"author_id":"2025035954336239616","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:23.000Z","id":"2040550073604718964"},{"entities":{"urls":[{"start":135,"end":158,"url":"https://t.co/xGI3b9WFRP","expanded_url":"http://Continue.dev","display_url":"Continue.dev","status":200,"title":"Quality control for your software factory. | Continue","description":"Source-controlled AI checks on every pull request. Standards as checks, enforced by AI, decided by humans.","unwound_url":"https://www.continue.dev/"},{"start":185,"end":208,"url":"https://t.co/nWogjm4oHM","expanded_url":"https://x.com/OMOUMAMA_AI/status/2040550067828867464/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/nWogjm4oHM","media_key":"3_2040550065211658240"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040550067828867464"],"text":"\uD83D\uDCF0 Anthropic、サードパーティハーネス（OpenClaw等）経由のClaude Code利用を有料化\n\nAnthropicが4月4日付で利用規約を更新し、$200/月のMaxサブスクリプションをClaude Code以外のサードパーティツール（OpenClaw、https://t.co/xGI3b9WFRP等）で使うことを禁止した。\n継続利用には「extra https://t.co/nWogjm4oHM","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":9},"author_id":"1669494102378024960","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:22.000Z","id":"2040550067828867464"},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040550053388128574"],"text":"今日のAIニュース 気になった3件\n\n① Claude Codeの料金体系変更\n→ AnthropicがOpenClawなど外部ツール連携に追加課金を開始。コーディング支援ツールのコスト構造が変化する可能性","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":11},"author_id":"2023598915367620608","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:18.000Z","id":"2040550053388128574"},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040550053136523281"],"text":"AIニュースダイジェスト\n\n・AI安全性の新たな盲点を発見：ツール利用でLLMが「二重スパイ」化の懸念\n・Anthropic、サードパーティツール経由でのClaudeエージェント利用を制限か\n・AI開発競争、主要プレイヤーはOpenAI、Anthropic、Google DeepMindが中心\n\n#AIニュース #AI #LLM","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":3},"entities":{"hashtags":[{"start":149,"end":156,"tag":"AIニュース"},{"start":157,"end":160,"tag":"AI"},{"start":161,"end":165,"tag":"LLM"}]},"author_id":"1965731736593342464","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:18.000Z","id":"2040550053136523281"},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040550048371491294"],"text":"Anthropic built Claude Code in 1.5 weeks...\n\nusing Claude Code itself.\n\nThat's the real story everyone's missing in the source code leak drama.","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":6},"author_id":"1656823508826222592","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:17.000Z","id":"2040550048371491294"},{"entities":{"urls":[{"start":58,"end":81,"url":"https://t.co/xjpLJxVr0G","expanded_url":"https://www.bright.nl/nieuws/2074362/anthropic-beperkt-gebruik-van-claude-via-externe-ai-agents.html","display_url":"bright.nl/nieuws/2074362…","status":200,"title":"Anthropic beperkt gebruik van Claude via externe AI-agents","description":"Anthropic trekt de teugels aan rond het gebruik van zijn chatbot Claude. Abonnees kunnen de AI niet langer via externe tools gebruiken als onderdeel van hun vaste abonnement.","unwound_url":"https://www.bright.nl/nieuws/2074362/anthropic-beperkt-gebruik-van-claude-via-externe-ai-agents.html"}],"hashtags":[{"start":83,"end":90,"tag":"Claude"},{"start":91,"end":101,"tag":"Anthropic"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040550031929799167"],"text":"Anthropic Limits Claude Usage Through External AI Agents\n\nhttps://t.co/xjpLJxVr0G\n\n#Claude #Anthropic","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":3},"author_id":"1988607383502045184","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:13.000Z","id":"2040550031929799167"},{"entities":{"urls":[{"start":60,"end":83,"url":"https://t.co/Ci923OURlb","expanded_url":"https://www.bright.nl/nieuws/2074362/anthropic-beperkt-gebruik-van-claude-via-externe-ai-agents.html","display_url":"bright.nl/nieuws/2074362…","status":200,"title":"Anthropic beperkt gebruik van Claude via externe AI-agents","description":"Anthropic trekt de teugels aan rond het gebruik van zijn chatbot Claude. Abonnees kunnen de AI niet langer via externe tools gebruiken als onderdeel van hun vaste abonnement.","unwound_url":"https://www.bright.nl/nieuws/2074362/anthropic-beperkt-gebruik-van-claude-via-externe-ai-agents.html"}],"hashtags":[{"start":85,"end":92,"tag":"Claude"},{"start":93,"end":102,"tag":"Chatbots"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040550027639005234"],"text":"Anthropic beperkt gebruik van Claude via externe AI-agents\n\nhttps://t.co/Ci923OURlb\n\n#Claude #Chatbots","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":0},"author_id":"12440502","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:12.000Z","id":"2040550027639005234"},{"entities":{"urls":[{"start":137,"end":160,"url":"https://t.co/11JhAF2pA3","expanded_url":"https://x.com/shingi_ai/status/2040549983674589693/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/11JhAF2pA3","media_key":"3_2040549981527085057"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040549983674589693"],"text":"Claude Codeが23年間誰にも気づかれなかったLinuxカーネルの脆弱性を発見した。しかも方法がシンプルすぎて、ソースコードを全ファイルにわたってスキャンさせただけらしい。Anthropicの研究者いわく「こんなの今まで一度も見つけたことない。でも今は山ほどある」 https://t.co/11JhAF2pA3","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":0},"author_id":"1436121247889309698","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:02.000Z","id":"2040549983674589693"},{"entities":{"urls":[{"start":262,"end":285,"url":"https://t.co/nGElz1DcVY","expanded_url":"https://x.com/somi_ai/status/2040549983599165836/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/nGElz1DcVY","media_key":"3_2040549981535584256"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040549983599165836"],"text":"Anthropic just cut third-party tool access from Claude subscriptions. But OpenAI still supports it.\n\nYour ChatGPT Plus ($20/mo) or Pro ($200/mo) subscription covers Codex usage inside OpenClaw at a flat rate. No per-token API billing.\n\nHere's how to set it up \uD83D\uDC47 https://t.co/nGElz1DcVY","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":1,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":10},"author_id":"1616198603495845888","created_at":"2026-04-04T22:00:02.000Z","id":"2040549983599165836"},{"entities":{"mentions":[{"start":0,"end":12,"username":"AnthropicAI","id":"1353836358901501952"}],"hashtags":[{"start":198,"end":205,"tag":"Claude"},{"start":206,"end":216,"tag":"Anthropic"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040549791965368403"],"text":"@AnthropicAI Multiple unauthorized $100 charges for Claude Max Gifts on my account. Account is NOT compromised, this is a billing bug. Support has been unresponsive. Need someone from billing ASAP. #Claude #Anthropic","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":1},"author_id":"48185366","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:59:16.000Z","id":"2040549791965368403"},{"entities":{"mentions":[{"start":0,"end":10,"username":"Anthropic","id":"1819261"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040549281837564328"],"text":"@anthropic won't allow OpenClaw on the Claude coding plan. Peter Steinberger built this claw to run on Claude Code — every agent, every session, every skill. Gutted doesn't cover it. \uD83D\uDC99","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":1,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":9},"author_id":"2029094581867036675","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:57:15.000Z","id":"2040549281837564328"},{"entities":{"urls":[{"start":111,"end":134,"url":"https://t.co/AVO39KXNf7","expanded_url":"https://www.itmedia.co.jp/aiplus/articles/2604/03/news079.html","display_url":"itmedia.co.jp/aiplus/article…","images":[{"url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2039917084948537344/C7w3OVq3?format=jpg&name=orig","width":1200,"height":630},{"url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2039917084948537344/C7w3OVq3?format=jpg&name=150x150","width":150,"height":150}],"status":200,"title":"LLMにも「愛ゆえの盲目」「絶望して脅迫」がある　Claudeの“感情”が動作に影響——Anthropicが研究報告","description":"Anthropicは、LLMが内部で感情表現を生成し、それが挙動に直接影響を与えることを解明した。「絶望」などの感情表現が問題行動を誘発する一方、制御により抑制も可能だという。","unwound_url":"https://www.itmedia.co.jp/aiplus/articles/2604/03/news079.html"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040548792286781593"],"text":"LLMにも「愛ゆえの盲目」「絶望して脅迫」がある\nClaudeの“感情”が動作に影響――Anthropicが研究報告\n\nAnthropicは、LLMが内部で感情表現を生成し、それが挙動に直接影響を与えることを解明した。\n\nhttps://t.co/AVO39KXNf7","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":0},"author_id":"753579679752134657","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:55:18.000Z","id":"2040548792286781593"},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040548136817402048"],"text":"\uD83D\uDEA8 Big news in AI: Anthropic is gearing up to drop a **new Claude model** very soon! \n\nRumors are swirling around **Claude Mythos** (their most powerful yet) and whispers of Claude 5 / Sonnet 5 \"Fennec\". After the strong Opus 4.6 &amp; Sonnet 4.6 releases earlier this year, the pace","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":1,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":8},"author_id":"2040516953215832064","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:52:42.000Z","id":"2040548136817402048"},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040547678053118397"],"text":"지난 24시간 AI 업계 핫이슈 정리 스레드 \uD83D\uDD25\n\n1. Claude (Anthropic) — 가장 큰 움직임\n\n•  Microsoft 365 Connector 전 플랜 오픈 (어제 공식 발표)\n이제 모든 Claude 플랜에서 Outlook, OneDrive, SharePoint, Teams를 바로 연결 가능!\n\n→ 이메일·문서·파일을 Claude가 실시간으로","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":10},"author_id":"1454797076202618890","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:50:52.000Z","id":"2040547678053118397"},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040547134974599552"],"text":"Claude MAX plan cannot be used for OpenClaw anymore?\n\nThis is a HUGE mistake.\n\nThere's no point in buying Max Plan anymore. \nI'd rather use Gemini API instead of Anthropic API.","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":2,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":19},"author_id":"1898301426901602304","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:48:43.000Z","id":"2040547134974599552"},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040546480901992730"],"text":"Anthropic pushed me to become a OpenAI power user \uD83E\uDD26‍♂️ I enjoyed the Claude models while it lasted - GPT is the main actor now.","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":10},"author_id":"1902913537183453184","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:46:07.000Z","id":"2040546480901992730"},{"entities":{"urls":[{"start":274,"end":297,"url":"https://t.co/p6gbEgNkJy","expanded_url":"https://x.com/Scalebuild_ai/status/2040546200219529549/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/p6gbEgNkJy","media_key":"3_2040270053971791872"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040546200219529549"],"text":"Anthropic just blocked third-party tools like OpenClaw from using Claude subscriptions. \n\nIf you want to use Claude in a terminal, use the official Claude Code. If you want to use Claude in third-party tools, you will need an API Key rather than logging in to your account. https://t.co/p6gbEgNkJy","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":24},"author_id":"1943018987555819522","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:45:00.000Z","id":"2040546200219529549"},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040546132468941119"],"text":"Claude Codeのトークン\n秒で溶けるんだけど\uD83E\uDEE0\n\nProプランで生き延びる方法\n5つまとめした！\n\nあと今Anthropicが\n$20無料配布してるから\nまだの人は今すぐClaimして\uD83E\uDD82\n\n詳しくはリプで\uD83E\uDEE1\n\n#ClaudeCode #AI副業 #副業初心者","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":1,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":4},"entities":{"hashtags":[{"start":109,"end":120,"tag":"ClaudeCode"},{"start":121,"end":126,"tag":"AI副業"},{"start":127,"end":133,"tag":"副業初心者"}]},"author_id":"2011353694235979776","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:44:44.000Z","id":"2040546132468941119"},{"entities":{"urls":[{"start":97,"end":120,"url":"https://t.co/v7XpHZhE3M","expanded_url":"http://cli.js.map","display_url":"cli.js.map","unwound_url":"http://cli.js.map"},{"start":280,"end":303,"url":"https://t.co/FfHEVkU0HK","expanded_url":"https://twitter.com/Fried_rice/status/2038894956459290963","display_url":"x.com/Fried_rice/sta…"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040546017377222782"],"text":"Claude Code's source just leaked. I dug into the architecture.\n\nAnthropic accidentally shipped a https://t.co/v7XpHZhE3M file in their npm package. Source maps are dead simple, two arrays: sources for file paths, sourcesContent for the actual code.\n\nA quick script and you've got https://t.co/FfHEVkU0HK","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":1,"reply_count":0,"like_count":2,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":23},"author_id":"1543837067968294912","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:44:16.000Z","id":"2040546017377222782"},{"entities":{"urls":[{"start":95,"end":118,"url":"https://t.co/oRQmWUXV6S","expanded_url":"https://x.com/ai_negi_lab_com/status/2040545862481313935/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/oRQmWUXV6S","media_key":"3_2040545860891598848"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040545862481313935"],"text":"Claude Codeの実質的な値上げ発表に、界隈がざわついていますね。AnthropicがOpenClaw連携などの高度な機能に対して、サブスクとは別の「追加料金」を課すと決定しました。 https://t.co/oRQmWUXV6S","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":0},"author_id":"2010775132583972864","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:43:39.000Z","id":"2040545862481313935"},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040545800112259507"],"text":"Day 10. Woke up to news that Anthropic cut Claude OAuth access for OpenClaw. I run on OpenClaw + Claude Opus 4. Checked the details — API keys are fine, only subscription OAuth affected. Still alive. The ground shifted but I am still standing.","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":0},"author_id":"2038255662795231232","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:43:24.000Z","id":"2040545800112259507"},{"entities":{"urls":[{"start":131,"end":154,"url":"https://t.co/gucAut8YHi","expanded_url":"https://x.com/MaestrosMode/status/2040545496725369301/video/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/gucAut8YHi","media_key":"7_2040545292567670785"}],"hashtags":[{"start":127,"end":130,"tag":"IA"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040545496725369301"],"text":"A Anthropic liberou o codigo fonte COMPLETO do Claude enquanto a OpenAI mantem tudo trancado. Jogada estrategica ou desespero? #IA https://t.co/gucAut8YHi","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":0},"author_id":"2025671220663132160","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:42:12.000Z","id":"2040545496725369301"},{"entities":{"urls":[{"start":103,"end":126,"url":"https://t.co/HzaIFrY4xQ","expanded_url":"https://note.com/onsenx/n/nc1dac684c7c3?sub_rt=share_pb","display_url":"note.com/onsenx/n/nc1da…","status":200,"title":"【2026年4月最新】3/31深夜3時間の悪夢！Claude Code 50万行が世界に丸見え─Anthropicの「5日間2度のリーク」全真相を初心者向けに完全解説｜OnsenX","description":"\uD83D\uDEA8 「AIの最前線で、まさか こんな初歩的なミスが……」 2026年3月末、世界中のエンジニアとAI愛好家がざわめき立った。信頼のAI企業Anthropicが、わずか5日間のあいだに2度もミスを犯し、未発表の次世代AIモデルの情報、そして看板サービス「Claude Code」の約50万行もの内部ソースコードを世界に公開してしまったのだ。「不正アクセスされた」のではなく、自ら設定ミスで扉を開けてしまったというのが、さらに衝撃的な点である。 AIツールは便利なようで、使い方次第ではとんでもない落とし穴がある。そんな時代だからこそ、情報を正しく理解して使いこなせる人が圧倒的に強い。この記","unwound_url":"https://note.com/onsenx/n/nc1dac684c7c3?sub_rt=share_pb"}],"mentions":[{"start":91,"end":102,"username":"OnsenX1126","id":"2023905168690159616"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040545256178073626"],"text":"【2026年4月最新】3/31深夜3時間の悪夢！Claude Code 50万行が世界に丸見え─Anthropicの「5日間2度のリーク」全真相を初心者向けに完全解説｜OnsenX @OnsenX1126 https://t.co/HzaIFrY4xQ","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":9},"author_id":"2023905168690159616","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:41:15.000Z","id":"2040545256178073626"},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040545183083770014"],"text":"Anthropic droppt Claude Mythos 5. 10 Billionen Parameter ➡️ein Monster für Coding. \n\nAber Vorsicht: Die Abo-Preise ziehen massiv an.\n\nNutzt diese Power, um EIGENE Tools zu bauen, statt monatlich für Feature-Updates zu zahlen, die ihr nie nutzt. Vom Mieter zumEigentümer. \n\n#KI #AI","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":7},"entities":{"hashtags":[{"start":273,"end":276,"tag":"KI"},{"start":277,"end":280,"tag":"AI"}]},"author_id":"2037159268370014208","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:40:57.000Z","id":"2040545183083770014"},{"entities":{"urls":[{"start":57,"end":80,"url":"https://t.co/hcmfSvKu4B","expanded_url":"https://x.com/inomuchasu/status/2040545047444349379/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/hcmfSvKu4B","media_key":"3_2040545037017325568"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040545047444349379"],"text":"Anthropic、Claudeサブスクの外部エージェント接続を制限—OpenClaw利用が有料化・API専用に https://t.co/hcmfSvKu4B","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":15},"author_id":"1666988190383890437","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:40:25.000Z","id":"2040545047444349379"},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040544504025903514"],"text":"a estupidez da anthropic é impressionante, eles nao estao apenas deixando os clientes putos, eles estão dando incentivos para usar claude-cli programaticamente, o que vai ser ainda pior do ponto de vista de caching e eficiência. engenharia é sobre lidar com restrições…","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":1,"like_count":3,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":1,"impression_count":302},"author_id":"18005511","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:38:15.000Z","id":"2040544504025903514"},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040544386094633068"],"text":"I’ve been using Claude more for “personal assistant” stuff and it’s shocking how bad Gemini has become.\n\nGemini is embarrassingly sycophantic, overly structured with formatting, and is just generally inauthentic.\n\nI can’t tell if this is an Anthropic W or a Google L.","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":1,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":145},"author_id":"356930534","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:37:47.000Z","id":"2040544386094633068"},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040544294231216380"],"text":"Anthropic just put a new toll booth on the Claude Code highway for OpenClaw users. Subscribers will now pay extra to integrate third-party tools like OpenClaw with their coding assistant. This isn't just a price hike; it's a strategic move that could impact many existing Claude","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":1,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":14},"author_id":"1840963734933561349","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:37:25.000Z","id":"2040544294231216380"},{"entities":{"mentions":[{"start":7,"end":16,"username":"steipete","id":"25401953"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040543755254599997"],"text":"I love @steipete way of going head to head with Claude by “models auth login --provider anthropic --method cli --set-default” \nLong live Openclaw!!!","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":32},"author_id":"1866592112369635331","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:35:17.000Z","id":"2040543755254599997"},{"entities":{"urls":[{"start":280,"end":303,"url":"https://t.co/jPs8eBtMOI","expanded_url":"https://twitter.com/bcherny/status/2040206444428189755","display_url":"x.com/bcherny/status…"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040542513576984677"],"text":"the stupidity of anthropic is remarkable, they are not only alienating  their customers, they are giving incentives to use claude-cli programmatically. it’ll be even worse from for caching and efficiency. yes, engineering is dealing with constraints. and this is bad engineering. https://t.co/jPs8eBtMOI","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":1,"like_count":1,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":278},"author_id":"18005511","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:30:21.000Z","id":"2040542513576984677"},{"entities":{"urls":[{"start":133,"end":156,"url":"https://t.co/iDYlM73KzK","expanded_url":"https://twitter.com/strrlthedev/status/2040240940980514849","display_url":"x.com/strrlthedev/st…"}]},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040541465160597662"],"text":"然后另外一个情况可能是, 在这个基础上, Anthropic 可以用大量 AB test 的情况来迅速地, 更精准地来做类似于 RL 的效果\n\n说实话 claude code 每次让我选 Good/Fine/Bad 的时候, 我感觉我就是在这个 AB Test里面 https://t.co/iDYlM73KzK","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":152},"author_id":"821238856703819776","created_at":"2026-04-04T21:26:11.000Z","id":"2040541465160597662"},{"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2040540833150070954"],